Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and word sense disambiguation.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses word embeddings and clustering algorithms.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with synonymy dictionaries and word sense induction, which are important for information retrieval tasks.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper uses graph-based approaches and clustering algorithms.
